                     <interp inst="t18151025-108-person901" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On Wednesday evening last, I searched, and found a silk handkerchief on him. I found on Mr. Ingleton's premises, this little tea caddy or box, broken open as it is now.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18151025-108-person902">
                  William 
                  Butler
               <interp inst="t18151025-108-person902" type="surname" value="Butler"></interp>
