                  </persName>
            . One of these four hats I know belongs to Connor, and this handkerchief I know to be mine. I think one of the other hats is Smedley's, because it was found at the door where we had the scuffle; and the other I think belongs to Bevers.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18151025-108-person903">
